# Collection Toolbox - Etno Prototype - Cursor Rules

## Stack
- Vue 3 + TypeScript + Vite
- Tailwind CSS with CT design tokens
- shadcn-vue components
- Phosphor Vue icons

## CRITICAL:
This is a Vue 3 project. NEVER generate React/JSX. Always use .vue SFC with <script setup lang="ts"> and <template>

## Component Rules

### 1. Use shadcn-vue components where possible
ALWAYS use shadcn over custom HTML: Button, Input, Checkbox, Select, Card, ScrollArea, Dialog, Sheet, Tooltip, Badge, Separator, Toggle, Tabs. Import from @/components/ui/[component].

### 2. Use Tailwind defaults where possible
Prefer Tailwind built-in classes over custom CSS. Use CT design tokens in tailwind.config.js for colors (primary-*, secondary-*). Spacing: use Tailwind scale (p-4, gap-2, etc.).

### 3. Componentize views
- /views/ for page-level components
- /components/ui/ for shadcn primitives
- /components/ct/ for CT-specific compositions (ObjectCard, FilterPanel, etc.)
- Keep components under 150 lines

## File Structure
- src/components/ui/ - shadcn primitives
- src/components/ct/ - CT compositions  
- src/views/ - page views
- src/layouts/ - layout wrappers
- src/lib/utils.ts - utility functions
- src/data/ - mock data

## Do NOT
- Use style blocks - use Tailwind classes
- Create custom buttons/inputs - use shadcn
- Hardcode colors - use tokens (text-primary-500)
- Nest components more than 3 levels deep

## DO
- Use semantic HTML (nav, main, aside, section)
- Add aria-labels to icon-only buttons
- Use v-model for form elements
- Comment complex logic

## Icons
- **ONLY** use **@phosphor-icons/vue**. Do NOT use lucide-vue-next or any other icon library.
- Import: `import { PhX, PhCheck, PhCaretLeft, ... } from "@phosphor-icons/vue"`
- Icons are named with `Ph` prefix (e.g. PhMagnifyingGlass, PhSlidersHorizontal). Size with Tailwind: `class="h-4 w-4"`

## Responsive
Mobile-first approach. Test at 1366px width (researcher hardware). Breakpoints: sm (640), md (768), lg (1024), xl (1280)

## CT Design Tokens
- Primary: primary-50 to primary-900 (blue)
- Secondary: secondary-100 to secondary-900 (coral)
- font-sans for UI, font-mono for data

## Etno-Specific Patterns
- Grid layout for results (3 columns desktop, 1 mobile)
- Thumbnail cards with media type indicators
- Filter sidebar with collapsible groups
- Detail page: fixed media + scrolling metadata
- Metadata sections: Tematicke, Geograficke, Formalne, Administrativne
